Spectools spectrum analyzer plugin

Both a handy visualizer for the output of the spectrum analyzer inside
Kismet, and an example for how to integrate a UI plugin with the main 
drawing window.

BUILD INSTRUCTIONS

For now, the plugin expects to be in a sub-directory of the Kismet 
newcore codebase.

INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS

run "make"

Copy spectools_ui.so to ~/.kismet/client_plugins/

USAGE

Run client
Kismet->Plugins->Add Plugin
Kismet->Plugins->Show Spectrum

